query:
UPDATE modules SET title = CASE 
  WHEN id = 6 THEN 'Session 4: Group Facilitation Skills'
  WHEN id = 7 THEN 'Session 5: Trauma-Informed Care'
  WHEN id = 8 THEN 'Session 6: Cultural Competency'
  WHEN id = 9 THEN 'Session 7: Ethics & Boundaries'
  WHEN id = 10 THEN 'Session 8: Crisis Intervention'
END WHERE id IN (6, 7, 8, 9, 10)
